# Install gui applications with homebrew-cask
tap caskroom/cask
install brew-cask
tap caskroom/versions # for iterm2 beta

# applications
cask install alfred
cask install android-device-filetransfer
cask install arduino
cask install atom
cask install dash
cask install dropbox
cask install firefox
cask install horndis
cask install iterm2
cask install java
cask install liteicon
cask install netspot
cask install spectacle
cask install steam
cask install transmission
cask install virtualbox
cask install vlc
cask install wireshark
cask install xquartz

# quicklook plugins
